{"tid":496953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 暗算 ] 男子在車內被紅纓槍插中，難道得罪了哪吒？","createTime":"2017-12-12T08:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:02:45.000Z","uid":53121,"like":188,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f094e12c3f4367fc25584995a840693b6b8720","tid":496953,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"中國安徽省黃山市一名男子，在12月8日深夜匆忙到黃山市人民醫院急診，驚人的是，他的背上竟然插著一桿紅纓槍，由於插入太深，醫院擔心拔出後會大出血，又急忙將他轉診到更好的醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n據《觀察者網》報導，這桿紅纓槍全長超過2公尺，警消到院後先協助將部分槍桿截斷。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>至於為何男子會中槍，目前只知道他在上車後被人暗算，有人從車後方隔著玻璃出槍，一槍貫穿玻璃後插入男子後</strong></span>背，至於詳細案情，當地警方仍在調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/163600_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F163600_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=42a147d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/163628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F163628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f6dbd445&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c671b5cfb37da888995b53a2ed016bf78b712430","tid":496953,"uid":86587,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"痴拿線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad26a8b0f9fddec8891dda4fcb9499fd4d53e17","tid":496953,"uid":53121,"like":202,"dislike":7,"score":195,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/163911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F163911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=50892820&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a9a89df676ffc2ab34e0c8fdec8072148e458a5","tid":496953,"uid":1